Package: mycolorsTB
Type: Package
Title: 'mycolorsTB': A Color Package for Mycobacterium tuberculosis Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Paula",
           family = "Ruiz-Rodriguez",
           email  = "paula.ruiz.rodriguez@csic.es",
           role   = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Colour palettes and helper functions for visualising
    Mycobacterium tuberculosis genomic and epidemiological data with
    'ggplot2' and 'ggtree'. The package provides predefined palettes,
    scale functions, tree/cladogram helpers, and convenient preview tools
    to ensure consistent branding in pathogen-omics visualisations. The
    palettes were developed as part of the mycolorsTB project
    <https://github.com/PathoGenOmics-Lab/mycolorsTB>.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    ape,
    ggtree
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
